577
00:48:03,974 --> 00:48:04,974
Six hours?

578
00:48:05,600 --> 00:48:07,894
My husband had a heart attack and died.

579
00:48:08,145 --> 00:48:09,145
What?!

580
00:48:11,107 --> 00:48:13,609
My husband had a heart attack...

581
00:48:13,860 --> 00:48:17,029
