582
00:48:18,698 --> 00:48:20,743
While we were making love.

583
00:48:21,910 --> 00:48:23,454
Holy shit!

584
00:48:23,704 --> 00:48:25,664
Jesus, Benjamin!

585
00:48:25,998 --> 00:48:28,751
